  "title": "Junior Business Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p>Role: Junior Business Operations Executive</p><p>Company: The Flower Factory</p><p>Location: Joo Chiat/Ubi</p><p>Employment Type: Full-time<br /></p><p><strong>About The Flower Factory</strong></p><p>The Flower Factory is a leading florist in Singapore founded in 2013. Our team believes in hard work, positive energy, and a passion for beautiful things. Led by an experienced entrepreneur with multiple successful exits, we're expanding beyond flower into new business areas, an exciting opportunity for those who want to learn and grow.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Can start immediately.</p></li><li><p>Diligent and responsible individual who can work 6-day work week; and on weekends.</p></li><li><p>No prior experience required: Fresh graduates or candidates with up to 3 years of relevant working experience are strongly preferred.</p></li><li><p>Graduated or graduating from a recognised institution, such as:</p><ul><li><p>China 985 / 211 universities</p></li><li><p>QS Top 50 universities</p></li><li><p>NUS / NTU / SMU</p></li><li><p>Singapore polytechnics with strong academic results<br /></p></li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>Job scope (More details to be given if you are short-listed for an interview.)</strong></p><ol><li><p>Assist CEO and manager with day to day operations of the florist shop, including various aspects of online and offline sales and after-sales.</p></li><li><p>Work with the CEO and manager to explore new online and offline sales and distribution channels.</p></li></ol><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><p>1. Strong pay package with great career growth prospects: Be part of a company that's evolving beyond floral business into multiple business ventures.<br />2. Mentorship from an Experienced CEO: Learn directly from a founder with multiple successful exits, ideal for fresh graduates or individuals who want to learn and grow.<br />3. Supportive Team Culture: Work with a passionate, hardworking yet down-to-earth team.</p><p><strong>Interested candidates please whatsapp your resume to </strong><a href=\"tel:+6581639692\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">+6581639692</a><strong>. Do not apply here.</strong></p>",
